title: United Kingdom Imports of Ores Slag & Ash
description: Imports of Ores, Slag & Ash in the United Kingdom increased to 267.55 GBP Million in September from 203.29 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Ores, Slag & Ash in the United Kingdom averaged 135.51 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 279.58 GBP Million in June of 2008 and a record low of 54.07 GBP Million in February of 2018. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Ores, Slag & Ash.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
